# Local/operator provider configuration (may reference env var names, never
# real secrets, but is still operator-specific and must not be committed).
# `.recollect/` above already covers repo-local and user-level config.{yaml,yml,json}.
# This covers the legacy repo-root default only -- anchored to the repo root
# so it does not hide the tracked examples/*/providers.json fixtures.
/providers.json
